'''Rony Rodrigues''' (Porto Alegre, April 30, 1979) is a Brazilian entrepreneur.

He is the founding partner of O’Grupo, a holding company with four companies:<ref>{{cite web|author=Germando Lüders/EXAME.com |url=http://exame.abril.com.br/revista-exame/edicoes/0982/noticias/jovens-irreverentes-e-disputados |title=Com OGrupo, foco em jovens - EXAME.com |publisher=Exame.abril.com.br |date=2010-12-15 |accessdate=2013-02-05}}</ref> Acquiris, electronic games; LiveAd, advertising; TalkInc, online research; and, Rony’s main focus, [[Box1824]], a research agency specialized in young people’s consumer and behavior trends.

==Career==

Rony Rodrigues began as an entrepreneur at age 17, when he opened a bar at the Planeta Atlântida festival. When he finished high school, he studied Tourism for a semester at Pontifícia Universidade Católica do Rio Grande do Sul (PUC-RS). When he returned to Brazil, Rony decided to work in advertising.<ref name="insighter">{{cite web|url=http://insighter.org/inovacao/a-historia-de-rony-rodrigues-socio-fundador-do-grupo-box-1824 |title=A história de Rony Rodrigues, sócio-fundador do Grupo Box 1824 |publisher=Insighter.Org |date= |accessdate=2013-02-05}}</ref> After a year in the segment, Rony won a [[Cannes Lions International Festival of Creativity|Cannes Lions award]], the first to be received by someone from Rio Grande do Sul{{Citation needed| date=February 2013}}. The ad that won him the prize was created for Senador, a local deodorant brand and consisted of a sticker that was glued on bus handrails with the following sentence: “Raise your hand if you use Senador.”{{Citation needed| date=February 2013}} In 2003, he founded Box1824 together with João Mognon Cavalcanti.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www1.folha.uol.com.br/folha/especial/2006/moda18/mo1108200606.shtml |title=Folha Online - Especial - 2006 - Moda 18 |publisher=.folha.uol.com.br |date=1970-01-01 |accessdate=2013-02-05}}</ref> In 2012, he was named one of the most innovative Brazilians in the digital segment by Proxxima magazine.<ref name="insighter" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://siterg.terra.com.br/moda/2011/05/09/meninos-do-brasil-mr-porter/ |title=Meninos do Brasil @Mr. Porter &#124; Site RG – Moda, Estilo, Festa, Beleza e mais – Terra |publisher=Siterg.terra.com.br |date=2011-03-29 |accessdate=2013-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213195332/http://siterg.terra.com.br/moda/2011/05/09/meninos-do-brasil-mr-porter/# |archive-date=2013-12-13 |dead-url=yes |df= }}</ref> In 2012, he also became a partner in an independent fashion brand, [[Cotton]] Project.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cottonproject.com.br/ |title=Cotton |publisher=Cottonproject.com.br |date= |accessdate=2013-02-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=2013 DLD13 |url=http://dld-conference.com/users/998 |title=DLD Conference Speaker: Rony Rodrigues |publisher=Dld-conference.com |date=2013-01-20 |accessdate=2013-02-05}}</ref>

==Box 1824==

In 2007, the agency Box 1824 was nominated for a Caboré Award, in the Specialized Services category. In 2009, it was also nominated for an Excellence Award for Best Paper in the market research conference, ESOMAR. Rony and Box 1824 have produced the videos We All Want to Be Young<ref name="economia">{{cite web|url=http://economia.ig.com.br/empresas/novo+uno+115+milhoes+de+opcoes+para+o+consumidor/n1237635935724.html |title=Novo Uno: 11,5 milhões de opções para o consumidor - Empresas - iG |publisher=Economia.ig.com.br |date=2010-05-29 |accessdate=2013-02-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://veja.abril.com.br/blog/ricardo-setti/tema-livre/video-bacana-o-que-diferencia-a-geracao-y/ |title=VĂdeo bacana: o que diferencia a GeraĂ§ĂŁo Y? &#124; Ricardo Setti - VEJA.com |publisher=Veja.abril.com.br |date=2012-09-30 |accessdate=2013-02-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Paloma M. Vazquez on November 22, 2010. @pmvazquez |url=http://www.psfk.com/2010/11/we-all-want-to-be-young.html |title=We All Want To Be Young |publisher=PSFK |date=2010-11-22 |accessdate=2013-02-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.semionaut.net/the-spirit-of-youth/ |title=The Spirit of Youth |publisher=Semionaut |date=2010-12-14 |accessdate=2013-02-05}}</ref> and All Work and All Play,<ref>{{cite web|author=Reprodução |url=http://exame.abril.com.br/marketing/noticias/box1824-lanca-all-work-and-all-play-sobre-o-comportamento-da-geracao-y |title=Box1824 lança "All work and all play", sobre o comportamento da Geração Y - EXAME.com |publisher=Exame.abril.com.br |date=2012-06-19 |accessdate=2013-02-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://publistagram.com/box-1824-all-work-and-all-play/ |title=Box 1824 - All work and all play |publisher=Publistagram |date=2012-06-19 |accessdate=2013-02-05}}</ref> um resumo dos resultados de diversos estudos realizados nos últimos 5 anos sobre o comportamento jovem, focados especialmente no grupo dos millennials,<ref>{{cite web |author=por harpersbazaar |url=http://harpersbazaar.